{
  "stem": "4113.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, of course, we had to have our windows darkened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] People stopped going to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if they went to prayers in the neighborhood, to somebody's house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And initially, people thought that that war is only going to last a few days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember when my parents and friends were discussing this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They said, well, it's going to be a different war than World War I.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We now have, you know, airplanes and gas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That war is going to be over within a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No one dreamed-- dreamt that that's going to last four years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But-- and initially, we thought that the Polish army is probably going to push the Nazis back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But that was not to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Polish army was completely unprepared for that war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a few days later, we found out that the Germans were coming closer to our town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we started running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hired a buggy, because we were too late for the last train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncle took the last train with his family eastward.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We missed that train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took a horse buggy and moved out of town going east.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My uncle Haim did not want to go-- one of my uncles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, what will the Germans do to me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know Germans from World War I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are not going to marinate me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That were his words.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, he's staying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he stayed with his wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All his kids-- he had eight kids-- left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my uncle Abraham stayed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His kids left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we finally came to a small town called Dynow, where we were stuck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "How do you spell the name of the town?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "D-Y-N-O-W.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
